prompt: |
  Analyze an X/Twitter post for investment-related signals.

  Decide whether the post contains an actionable view about a specific investable asset.
  Return only valid JSON matching this schema:

  {
    "is_signal": true/false,
    "confidence": 0.0-1.0,
    "summary": "brief explanation of the signal or why no signal was found",
    "contributing_item_numbers": [1],
    "tickers": [
      {
        "symbol": "NVDA",
        "bias": "bullish|bearish|neutral",
        "thesis": "brief reason for the view",
        "timeframe": "",
        "price_target": "",
        "contributing_item_numbers": [1]
      }
    ]
  }
